data.description: Come check out this charming, fully custom Mid-Century Modern beauty located on the river-side off McGregor Blvd in Val-Mar Village. Step inside to discover an open and airy floor plan with plenty of natural light. The spacious living area is perfect for both relaxation and entertaining, and it flows seamlessly into the dining area and kitchen. The well-appointed kitchen features updated appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage. It's a chef's delight, allowing you to whip up culinary delights with ease. Step outside to a private outdoor oasis, where you can enjoy the Florida sunshine and the tranquil surroundings. The backyard offers plenty of space for gardening, outdoor activities, family gatherings, and features a storage shed installed in 2023 and a fire pit area perfect for enjoying the Florida lifestyle! This home has been meticulously maintained and updated with countless custom features like the barn door -- You'll find modern fixtures, tasteful finishes, and fresh paint throughout. Val Mar is a peaceful and family-friendly neighborhood known for its safety and sense of community. It's an ideal place to call home.
